      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just \"interference\" though. like, why would they name it that specific thing unless they were trying to let me know? and it's way too consistent. every single time i go in there, the bars drop or spike. it feels way more deliberate than just random waves. dont u think the timing is a bit too suspicious for it to be a coincidence?",
