    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i tried looking into the building materials thing but my walls are just standard drywall. it doesn't explain why the name is a direct reference to my movements. i'm starting to think they might have some kind of sensor linked to the router that pings when motion is detected in my kitchen. if they were using something like that to monitor me, how would they even hide it so a normal person wouldn't notice?",
